rc=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T08:08:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 知收信人叫咩名就faithfully，唔知就sincerely"},{"pid":"b85b051dc85dcb02ad3691e5d33baa3c258375b3","tid":864270,"uid":156652,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T08:08:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZT9Zpxv.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZT9Zpxv.gif&h=c4ff8c06&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"86871625eae75a826882f5043ab3256dbfcfca8e","tid":864270,"uid":25992,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T08:08:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n點解係faithfully唔係sincerely?</blockquote>係唔係代表我識你老鼠呀？</blockquote>我記得以前個英文老師係教 非親非故faithfully<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 知收信人叫咩名就faithfully，唔知就sincerely好似係</blockquote>"},{"pid":"f75a6797f79bfaa4a2de1a588c8a4a2a481f741f","tid":864270,"uid":168366,"like":40,"dislike":1,"score":39,"quote":{"pid":"8c67414627706a5930a7a8b370515d814b223e34","tid":864270,"uid":168366,"like":11,"dislike":30,"score":-19,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T06:54:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n點解係faithfully唔係sincerely?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T08:09:53.000Z","msg":"做咩咁多負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\ngoogle左中外幾個網都咁講<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.masteringgrammar.com/2012/05/yours-sincerely-yours-faithfully.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.masteringgrammar.com%2F2012%2F05%2Fyours-sincerely-yours-faithfully.html&d=cEAnvk2AvDxxfsjQNXhyCgCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=f6fa6b1b\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.masteringgrammar.com/2012/05/yours-sincerely-yours-faithfully.html</a><br />\n<br />\n&quot;Yours sincerely&quot; 和 &quot;Yours faithfully&quot; 都是用於正式信結尾簽名前的套語，但它們並不是隨便可以交換用的。如果我們以收信人的姓氏相稱呼 (如 Dear Mr. Wong，Dear Ms. Lee 等等)，我們會用 &quot;Yours sincerely&quot;。假若我們以 &quot;Dear Sir/Madam&quot; 或 &quot;Dear Parents&quot; 等沒有名字的字眼去稱呼收信人，我們則會用 &quot;Yours faithfully&quot;。<br />\n<br />\n&quot;Yours sincerely&quot; 語氣上比較親切，而 &quot;Yours faithfully&quot; 則比較疏遠。"},{"pid":"21ae1fbc23b329e68f9840ec8a468213584eb2ba","tid":864270,"uid":168366,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T08:11:22.000Z","msg":"BBC<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/learningenglish/youmeus/learnit/learnitv153.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fworldservice%2Flearningenglish%2Fyoumeus%2Flearnit%2Flearnitv153.shtml&d=cEAnvk2AvDxxfsjQNXhyCgCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=ac37fbe6\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/learningenglish/youmeus/learnit/learnitv153.shtml</a><br />\n<br />\nIf you don't know the person you are writing to so well, but know of him as a named individual, start with title and surname: Dear Mr Potter or Dear Dr Baker or Dear Miss Taylor or Dear Mrs Cook or Dear Ms Barber. If you are not sure which of the last three titles is appropriate in any particular case, it is probably best to stick to Ms.<br />\n<br />\nFinish this type of letter with Yours sincerely. <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nIf you do not know the name of the person you are writing to, begin with Dear Sir or Dear Sir or Madam or Dear Madam and end your letter with Yours faithfully, followed by your full name and designation."},{"pid":"db883a34d13619696a6297a62f70c3b44ce0ac76","tid":864270,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T08:11:37.000Z","msg":"propaganda<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a934632191fc13b0dc27a1d8e78857f5741a783c","tid":864270,"uid":5178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T08:12:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"450332b38d1760bcb1797192015e82197070ae8c","tid":864270,"uid":3659,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T08:15:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/16/161441_6e0c970a6dbbf5c0c643e0e96ce35230.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F16%2F161441_6e0c970a6dbbf5c0c643e0e96ce35230.gif&h=4f9b54cd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"eb53443ed63b1dc54b0d59b7634773d7d2be125b","tid":864270,"uid":92301,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"81cad563bc8da51af154eff0d08fa9810bc5543b","tid":864270,"uid":27688,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T05:40:20.000Z","msg":"8月30日？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T09:50:03.000Z","msg":"On 15 October, Chinese-language newspaper Ta Kung Pao published extracts of a letter from Acting Consul-General Esther Blythe to the Editor regarding UK engagement with local civil society organisations and academics. In the interests of transparency, we are publishing the letter in full.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1981721321871286&amp;id=153101271399976\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D1981721321871286%26id%3D153101271399976&d=cEAnvk2AvDxxfsjQNXhyCgCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=79fe20b6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1981721321871286&amp;id=153101271399976</a>"},{"pid":"da9ae2e1009be9ecb80fbb08bb7d9d609157b42