","tid":864270,"uid":184726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f75a6797f79bfaa4a2de1a588c8a4a2a481f741f","tid":864270,"uid":168366,"like":40,"dislike":1,"score":39,"quote":{"pid":"8c67414627706a5930a7a8b370515d814b223e34","tid":864270,"uid":168366,"like":11,"dislike":30,"score":-19,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T06:54:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n點解係faithfully唔係sincerely?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T08:09:53.000Z","msg":"做咩咁多負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\ngoogle左中外幾個網都咁講<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.masteringgrammar.com/2012/05/yours-sincerely-yours-faithfully.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.masteringgrammar.com%2F2012%2F05%2Fyours-sincerely-yours-faithfully.html&d=cEAnvk2AvDxxfsjQNXhyCgCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=f6fa6b1b\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.masteringgrammar.com/2012/05/yours-sincerely-yours-faithfully.html</a><br />\n<br />\n&quot;Yours sincerely&quot; 和 &quot;Yours faithfully&quot; 都是用於正式信結尾簽名前的套語，但它們並不是隨便可以交換用的。如果我們以收信人的姓氏相稱呼 (如 Dear Mr. Wong，Dear Ms. Lee 等等)，我們會用 &quot;Yours sincerely&quot;。假若我們以 &quot;Dear Sir/Madam&quot; 或 &quot;Dear Parents&quot; 等沒有名字的字眼去稱呼收信人，我們則會用 &quot;Yours faithfully&quot;。<br />\n<br />\n&quot;Yours sincerely&quot; 語氣上比較親切，而 &quot;Yours faithfully&quot; 則比較疏遠。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T11:34:39.000Z","msg":"因為真係唔想同大公報啲人咁熟，影衰自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"508773bc5bc249f9080ccce5218196565a444c31","tid":864270,"uid":99205,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T11:40:43.000Z","msg":"係我話<br />\n下款就留FUCK U就算"},{"pid":"575e91b57ea2b42ac59a81d9df888390168fdcd3","tid":864270,"uid":190928,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T11:50:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/16/194958_7cb176f528745fa56d961e620c8